-- Transelectrica to Spend $750 Million on Improvements, ZF Reports
-- B y   I r i n a   S a v u
-- 2012-01-24T07:26:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-24/transelectrica-to-spend-750-million-on-improvements-zf-reports.html
Transelectrica SA (TEL) , a Romanian power-
grid operator, plans to spend 2.5 billion lei ($750 million)
over 2012-2014 on improvements and projects,  Ziarul Financiar
 reported.  The state-owned utility will invest 782 million lei in 2012
and try to borrow 1.2 billion lei from banks to fund spending
over the period, the Bucharest-based newspaper said, without
disclosing where it got the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Irina Savu in Bucharest at 
 isavu@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  